Modification notice (2026-07-13):

The upstream project was reduced to a standalone Agent Skill named
"format-content". The modified workflow accepts only Markdown text or a
readable .md file, always uses the red-and-white theme, emits a validated
clean section fragment plus a copy-button preview, and never publishes to
WeChat. Non-Markdown normalization, theme selection, theme generation, and
all other themes were removed from this distribution.

